<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome <%= @user_invitation %></h1>
    <p>
      Someone has invited you to join. You can join by following the link
      below:

      http://localhost:3000/users/register?invite_code=<%= @user_invitation.invite_code %>

      If you are not a member then you can sign up or you can log use an
      existing account if you have one.
    </p>
    <p>
      If the link doesn't work then go to http://localhost:3000/users/register
      and enter the invitation code <%= @user_invitation.invite_code %>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>